1
00:00:04,333 --> 00:00:09,541
Before using a device, take note of the power socket, reset button, and LED lights.

2
00:00:13,708 --> 00:00:17,541
Some devices have the power socket, button and LED lights on an external wire.

3
00:00:18,166 --> 00:00:21,083
Other devices have these areas covered.

4
00:00:23,125 --> 00:00:26,458
Plug in the supplied power supply to power up the device before using it.

5
00:00:27,875 --> 00:00:32,000
If the device has never been paired, the LEDs will alternately flash and wait to be paired.

6
00:00:35,291 --> 00:00:36,125
How to pair the device to my account？

7
00:00:37,125 --> 00:00:45,875
Open the app, log in, click the Add Device button, and select the type of device you want to add.

8
00:00:46,458 --> 00:00:48,250
QR code is the most common and easiest way to set.

9
00:00:49,416 --> 00:00:54,208
If the LED of the device is not flashing alternately, you can press and hold the reset button to reset it first.

10
00:00:54,000 --> 00:01:00,916
Enter your password when setting Wi-Fi  and the username will automatically use the one your phone is currently connected to.

11
00:01:01,375 --> 00:01:05,000
If you wish to change your Wi-Fi connection or it is 5G，click the change button.

12
00:01:06,333 --> 00:01:09,916
Next step, a QR code will appear on your App.

13
00:01:09,250 --> 00:01:14,666
Place this QR code 3-8 inches in front of the lens of your device and let the camera scan it.

14
00:01:15,916 --> 00:01:19,000
If the scan is not successful, you can move your phone slightly up and down, back and forth.

15
00:01:19,625 --> 00:01:22,958
When the scan is complete, you will hear a prompt and click "Next".

16
00:01:22,125 --> 00:01:27,625
If having trouble scanning the QR code, double click on the QR code to zoom in and this may make scanning easier.

17
00:01:29,750 --> 00:01:31,291
Please wait for the device to pair automatically.

18
00:01:32,833 --> 00:01:35,875
When it is done, you can rename the device to your preference.

19
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:46,208
After pairing is complete,  enter the device home list and you can see the added devices,  play live, replay recordings, and adjust settings and other functions.
